     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Cyberpunk theme. Neon pink (#FF007A),
         electric purple (#9B59B6), and cyan (#00FFEA) accents on a near-black
         (#0D0D0D) background with glowing highlight effects.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in CyberpunkTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

